text: Saint-Julien-en-Champsaur is a commune in the Hautes-Alpes department. == Population == == Transport == === Road === The D15, D43, D215, D243 and D945 roads pass through the commune. == Notable people == Vivian Maier used to live in Saint-Julien-en-Champsaur. == References == Category:Communes in Hautes- Alpes
